245
00:16:31,702 --> 00:16:34,452
and even economists and lawyers.

246
00:16:34,452 --> 00:16:40,099
But I think designing
and developing spacecrafts

247
00:16:40,099 --> 00:16:42,549
are very attractive to me,

248
00:16:42,549 --> 00:16:46,388
so I decided to become
an aerospace engineer.

249
00:16:46,388 --> 00:16:48,204
And becoming an astronaut

250
00:16:48,204 --> 00:16:51,604
it's my long-term dream 
since my childhood,

251
00:16:51,604 --> 00:16:53,647
so I tried and tried.

